enhanced_by.reason: The method allSupportedLocales() provides the list of locales from which localeStringWithRandom() selects a random locale.

Both methods select a locale at random, but localeStringWithoutReplacement() does so without replacement, which can inform the assertions for localeStringWithRandom() regarding the randomness and uniqueness of the selection.
The displayName() method also deals with locale selection and formatting, which can inform the assertions for localeStringWithRandom() regarding the expected format of the returned locale string.
